minimumRequirement: Minimum ten (10) characters (maximum one hundred (100) characters)
characterRequirement: Must contain a minimum of five (5) unique characters
caseRequirement: Must contain, at least, the following characters: One (1) uppercase, one (1) lowercase, one (1) number and one (1) special character (~ ! @ # $ % ^ * - _ = + [ { ] } / ; : , . ?)
confirmationStepDescriptionAuth: In order to change your password, you must first enter the confirmation code you see on your Authenticator App.
confirmationStepDescriptionSMS: In order to change your password, you must first enter a security code which will be sent via text.
